<note n="0341004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0341004">唯＝惟【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0341005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0341005"><g ref="#CB00450">䨥</g>＝雙【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0342001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0342001">故＝是【元】</note>
<note n="0342002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0342002">起＝趣【三】【宮】</note>
